Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.85,0:03:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接發給我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just email it to me directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事對我太重要  不容有失\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is too important for me to miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威利克先生  我們到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Wellick, we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.54,0:04:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次能給我300塊錢嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think I could have 300 this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.73,0:04:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真像個資本主義者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Spoken like a true capitalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作不順嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bad day at the office?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.31,0:04:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No ki--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  別打了  停\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, enough. No more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.30,0:05:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大多數程序員都認為軟件除漏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Most coders think debugging software
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是修正錯誤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is about fixing a mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:05:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這是胡扯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but that's bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除漏的關鍵其實是找到錯漏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Debugging's actually all about finding the bug,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理解這個漏洞從何而來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about understanding why the bug was there to begin with,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及明白漏洞的出現并非偶然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about knowing that its existence was no accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.21,0:06:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漏洞向你傳達了信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It came to you to deliver a message,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像一個毫無意識的氣泡浮出水面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}like an unconscious bubble floating to the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆出你可能早就心知肚明的真相\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}popping with a revelation you've secretly known all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.99,0:06:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道我為什么說這些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know why I'm saying all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是因為打了太多禮來制藥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe it's because I'm pumped up on whatever---
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用來圈錢的  不知道什么合法藥品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}legal drug dealers like Eli Lilly make money off nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過一般是因為我預見到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But usually it's because there's a sense it's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正有只蟲子[漏洞]朝我飛來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A bug buzzing its way towards me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.36,0:06:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攪得我不得安寧  逼我作出決定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to gum up the works until it forces me to make a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了我還是接受我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kill me or embrace me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又或者我只是有點嚇著了  因為我沒想到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or maybe I'm just freaking out because I never thought
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會醒來看到這兩個女人盯著我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd wake up to find these two women staring back at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說不清\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幾個小時前剛來時  你我還說過話呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We talked maybe a few hours ago when I first got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說我是你的緊急聯絡人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They said I was your emergency contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  你還要他們聯系你的心理醫生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right. Um, you told them to call your psychiatrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有咨詢了心理醫生之后你才能出院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't leave until you talk to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去等著了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So I'm gonna wait outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得你向醫務人員點名聯系我嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you remember requesting me from the staff?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我來是因為警察說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You requested me because the police said that--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被幾個小青年偷襲了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got jumped by a bunch of kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什么大不了的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們要做全面的藥檢  你拒絕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They wanted to do a full drug panel, and you refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能問問原因嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}May I ask why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:08:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾略特  如果我們都不能好好談談的話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elliot, if we can't have a conversation about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在用嗎啡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've been taking morphine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.12,0:08:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒什么合理的理由給你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't have a good enough reason to give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望有  但我沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish I did, but I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許你應該去戒毒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe we should consider rehab.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是癮君子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not a junkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你得證明給我看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then you'll need to prove it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.28,0:08:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每兩個月自愿參加一次藥檢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Submit to a bimonthly drug test voluntarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這樣我才會同意你出院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the only way that I'll recommend your release.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hospitals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣高度聯網的機構\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A heavily networked one like this
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑進去太輕松了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are almost too easy to hack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是威廉·海斯密斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is William Highsmith.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不止是這家醫院技術部門的頭頭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's not only the head of the IT department here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還是整個部門唯一的員工\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he is the IT department.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還是個白癡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's also an idiot,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我倒不怨他  因為雇用他的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not that I blame him because the people that hired him
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是一群白癡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are also idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可憐鬼每年只有7000塊左右的預算\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The poor guy only gets a budget of about 7,000 bucks a year,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑他還想保護自家網絡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and he's supposed to protect their network
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不被我這樣的人黑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}from people like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點機會都沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He never stood a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他用Windows98系統上沒用的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He uses useless virus scans, dated servers,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病毒掃描軟件  過時服務器和安全軟件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and security software that runs on Windows 98.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是因為這一點  才指定這家醫院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's one of the reasons why I made this place
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.08,0:09:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為我的優先收治醫院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}my primary care facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}藥品檢測  陽性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.77,0:09:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以把我的病歷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can make my health records
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.04,0:09:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改得就像那些順從的活死人一樣正常\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}look like every other obedient zombie out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}陰性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.01,0:09:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用擔心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再嗑嗎啡了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not gonna do morphine again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.82,0:09:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這兒有火柴嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, you got some matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.30,0:09:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}能量飲料  無糖  低卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這早餐真簡單\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a nice breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  信用卡刷不了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry. Credit card system is down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.96,0:09:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}由于邪惡公司最近的入侵事故  本店信用卡系統無法使用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如我所說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除漏最難的一點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the most difficult thing about debugging
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是修補漏洞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}isn't fixing the bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}大規模黑客攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.08,0:09:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是找到漏洞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all about finding the bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對于邪惡公司\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For Evil Corp,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機器人先生通過我找到了他們的漏洞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Robot found their bug in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是那個觸發了這一切的錯漏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was the mistake that led to all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事我得問問你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to ask you one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.39,0:10:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維拉被抓和你有關系嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you have something to do with Vera getting busted?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見鬼  艾略特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shit, Elliot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說了你不會插手的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said you weren't gonna do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他被控殺人罪了  你知道嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's on murder charges, do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.96,0:10:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他手下的人都完蛋了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His whole crew bounced.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在也不知道去哪掙錢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, I don't know what I'm gonna do for money now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我吧  艾略特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just tell me, Elliot,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別撒謊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and don't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.26,0:10:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了這么多事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, with everything that happened--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.57,0:10:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的門怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened to your door?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不該在這里的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not supposed to be here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:11:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我換鎖是有原因的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I changed the locks for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩具挺有意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Interesting toy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.11,0:11:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你還是得多花點心思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but you may want to spend a little more scratch
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能指望這玩意兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if you actually want it to, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖得住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.32,0:11:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Check it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}絕不退縮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰西卡·阿爾芭說她想加入去社會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jessica Alba says she wants to join fsociety.
