Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單把注意力集中在記錄上還不夠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}{\*}It's not enough just to focus your attention on the logs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還得時刻關注社交媒體的動向\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We should also monitor social media traffic
