Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.90,0:15:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你準備告訴我發生了什么嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want to tell me what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not really. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你翹班  然后這個樣子出現\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're missing work, you come in looking like that,
