Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.33,0:24:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的照片  畫什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}like from my photographs or drawings and--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.57,0:24:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like, there's this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.07,0:24:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺老套的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Um, it's really f---ing corny,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.75,0:24:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但上面什么都有  孩子什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but, like, it has everything-- the kids and the...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.77,0:24:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏拉的漏洞我一直捉摸不透\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shayla's bug was always elusive to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.65,0:24:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許就是這個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe this was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.34,0:24:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渴望正常  卻卡在邊緣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wanting normalcy but stuck in the outer fringes,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.52,0:24:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知該如何參與進去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not knowing how to participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.95,0:24:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.06,0:24:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能吻你嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I kiss you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.17,0:24:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次別問了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Next time, don't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.95,0:24:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太傻了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.92,0:25:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漏洞一向名聲不好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bugs usually get a bad rap.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.29,0:25:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有時候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.20,0:25:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓我失望  好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't let me down, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.20,0:25:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當一個漏洞終于顯現\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When a bug finally makes itself known,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.00,0:25:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會讓人興奮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it can be exhilarating,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.21,0:25:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你剛剛解鎖了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}like you just unlocked something.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.58,0:25:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個美好的機會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A grand opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.48,0:25:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等著你去利用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}waiting to be taken advantage of.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.75,0:25:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威利克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Wellick?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.80,0:25:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么來著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What was your name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.21,0:25:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安瓦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anwar.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.03,0:25:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你也來這種地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't know you came to places like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.07,0:25:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.44,0:25:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思  你不是來了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you mean? You're here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.71,0:25:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來是因為你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm here because you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.99,0:25:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  抱歉  我不懂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What? Sorry, I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.43,0:25:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你很美  我想帶你回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think you're beautiful. I want to take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.86,0:25:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你不是結婚了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait, I thought you were married.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.65,0:26:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  畢竟  漏洞唯一的作用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because, after all, a bug's only purpose,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.51,0:26:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它存在的唯一原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}its only reason for existence
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.46,0:26:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是作為等待修補的錯誤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is to be a mistake that needs fixing,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.38,0:26:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫你糾正錯誤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to help you right a wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.76,0:26:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么比這感覺更棒的呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what feels better than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.29,0:26:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾略特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}{\*}So, Elliot,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.15,0:26:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不介紹一下嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}do you think you should introduce us?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.79,0:26:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏拉  這是安吉拉和奧利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, um, Shayla, this is Angela and Ollie.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.71,0:26:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今晚很美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You, uh, you look lovely this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.07,0:26:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  伙計們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What up, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.39,0:26:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們才到嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You just get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.03,0:26:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西裝不錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nice suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.36,0:26:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了  伙計\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.94,0:26:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-該死  -你是怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Shit. - What is up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.41,0:26:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這一晚上都煩躁不安的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've been fidgeting all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.70,0:26:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們再按一次門鈴吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe we should try the doorbell again.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.10,0:27:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.12,0:27:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們站多久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long have you been standing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.66,0:27:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門鈴壞了  我該說一聲的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The doorbell is broken. I should have warned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.84,0:27:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進吧  我是哈利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come in. I'm Harry, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.71,0:27:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-安吉拉  認識你很高興  -認識你很高興\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Angela. Nice to meet you. - Good to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.94,0:27:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高興終于能對上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Always nice to put a face... 
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.20,0:27:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,員工號和臉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with an employee badge number, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.83,0:27:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧利  你們在一起多久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ollie, how long have you guys been together?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.70,0:27:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-兩年半  -兩年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- 2 1/2 years. - 2 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.11,0:27:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.38,0:27:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾略特  你和夏拉在一起多久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elliot, how long have you and Shayla been together?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.78,0:27:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, uh, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.46,0:27:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就今天才開始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}j-just today.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.15,0:27:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你審夠客人了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, enough grilling of the guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.57,0:27:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去看看烤爐吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's check on the real grill, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.66,0:27:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾略特  幫幫忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elliot, I could use your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.59,0:27:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要向你承認件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So I have a confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.57,0:27:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓杜勒斯數據中心的系統管理員\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had the sys admins at the data center in Dulles
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.54,0:28:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又去看了一遍那個服務器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}check that server again.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.13,0:28:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉迪恩  你做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gideon, what did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.03,0:28:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了  根本沒找到什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course there was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.88,0:28:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真不知道我為什么要起疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have no idea what there was to even be suspicious about.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.93,0:28:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會有什么動機\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, what possible motivation would you have
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.29,0:28:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去搞破壞  我大概只是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to do anything? I guess I was just being--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.88,0:28:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉迪恩必須放手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gideon has to let this go.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.54,0:28:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他靠近這個馬蜂窩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If he comes near this hornet's nest,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.17,0:28:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道我是不是能救下他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not sure I can save him from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.41,0:28:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得消除他任何的疑慮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to kill any suspicion left.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.53,0:28:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在眾安一直努力工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've been nothing but a hard worker for Allsafe,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.65,0:28:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我道歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.08,0:28:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在飛機上聊過之后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After the conversation on the plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.35,0:28:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認識到這關系到整個公司的命運\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I knew what was at stake-- the whole company.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.85,0:28:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擔心我找到的dat文件并不是要緊的那個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was worried that the dat file I found wasn't the right one.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.94,0:28:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是不想...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.62,0:28:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你抱有希望  以免是我錯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}want to get your hopes up in case I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.41,0:28:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以會面之前我并沒跟你說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's why I didn't tell you before the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.43,0:28:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.69,0:29:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得讓他抱我了  是嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna have to let him hug me, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.31,0:29:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個優秀的工程師  艾略特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're such a brilliant engineer, Elliot,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.19,0:29:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你絕對不要懷疑自己的才華\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you should never doubt your skills
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.90,0:29:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管我給了你多大壓力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}no matter how much pressure I put on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.25,0:29:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你更不用對我有所隱瞞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you certainly don't have to keep anything from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.17,0:29:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我關心你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I care about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.49,0:29:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《巴茲爾弗蘭維勒太太的混亂檔案》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From the Mixed-up Files of Basil E. Frankweiler.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.64,0:29:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是受了那個的啟發  記得嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's where I got the idea, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.10,0:29:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是那么想做克勞迪婭·金凱德{\fs14}[書中人物]\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanted to be Claudia Kincaid so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.91,0:29:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連她的名字都那么酷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even her name was cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.87,0:30:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得嗎  我們以為我們是去的大都會博物館\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Remember we thought we were going to the Met,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.20,0:30:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果不知卻怎么跑到了皇后區博物館\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}somehow we ended up at the Queens Museum instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.01,0:30:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時可沒有谷歌地圖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No Google Maps back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.03,0:30:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡跟你離家出走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I loved running away with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.66,0:30:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八歲的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Somehow when you're eight,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.99,0:30:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離家出走還挺好玩的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}running away can be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.46,0:30:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.12,0:30:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說說笑笑  赴晚宴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Smiles, dinner parties,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.33,0:30:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,童年回憶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}childhood stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.30,0:30:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以習慣這樣的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I could get used to this,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.32,0:30:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至喜歡上它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}maybe even like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.63,0:30:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.90,0:30:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...入侵丑聞仍在繼續\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Corp's hacking scandal continues
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.72,0:31:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在又有大量電郵被放出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with the release of these latest emails.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.33,0:31:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}首席技術官泰瑞·科比涉嫌與93年泄露事件有關  邪惡公司遭竊數據顯示重大掩蓋事件
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.85,0:31:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據最新遭披露的資料顯示\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Information stemming from the latest dump reveals
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.56,0:31:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰瑞·科比與另外兩位高管\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that Terry Colby was one of three high-level executives
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.78,0:31:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共同參與了掩蓋廣為人知的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}involved in the cover-up of the widely publicized
